  &lt;p id="97QfaU"&gt;Roku is &lt;a href="https://newsroom.roku.com/news/2024/08/new-roku-sports-channel-brings-viewers-24-7-access-to/y4xvizai-1722959304"&gt;preparing to launch&lt;/a&gt; a new 24/7 sports channel across its devices, apps, and on its website. Starting on August 12th, the new Roku Sports Channel will start showing sports-themed content that includes live events and original content.&lt;/p&gt;
